item.title: Genius: '14 Years Of Jay Z Rapping About His Love For Beyoncé'
item.description: It’s hard to believe there was a time when Beyoncé and Jay Z were hush-hush about their love affair. Yet back in the early 2000s, the two budding superstars treated relationship rumors like an MC Hammer auto loan: denied, denied, denied. Once the power couple went public, though, they’d flaunt their union on-wax at virtually every possible opportunity.

item.title: Life Noggin: 'Why Do You Sleepwalk?'
item.description:
